Articles.Content:
Join Ozzy, as he constructs his plasma-thruster based interplanetary space craft, assembling the various parts needed in low Kerbin orbit! 

This space craft will be the catalyst for rescuing our crew out at Eeloo, as well as gathering ever valuable scientific data!

[http://www.twitch.tv/ozzyinspace](http://www.twitch.tv/ozzyinspace) <- See you there! 11am CST

- Ozzy

(can you believe this name wasn't taken?)
